1. PURPOSE
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This license allows you to use and share this software for noncommercial
purposes for free, to use it commercially for free below the revenue threshold
in Section 7.4, and requires a revenue contribution for larger commercial
operations to sustain ongoing development. This software is source-available;
this is not an open-source license as defined by the Open Source Initiative.

