2. DEFINITIONS
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

"Licensor" means Gestura AI LLC, a Delaware limited liability company.

"Software" means the software this license is distributed with, in source or
compiled form, including any portion of it and any modification of it.

"You" and "Your" mean the individual or legal entity exercising rights under
this license, together with all Affiliates.

"Affiliate" means any entity that controls, is controlled by, or is under
common control with You, where "control" means ownership of more than fifty
percent (50%) of voting interests or the power to direct management.

"Use" means anything you do with the Software requiring one of the license
grants in Sections 4 or 5, including copying, running, modifying,
distributing, offering as a service, and embedding in a product.

"Commercial Use" means any Use intended for or directed toward commercial
advantage or monetary compensation, including internal business use.

"Noncommercial Use" means any Use that is not Commercial Use.

"Gross Revenue" means all revenue of You and Your Affiliates, as recognized
under the accounting standard You ordinarily apply (GAAP, IFRS, or national
equivalent), before any deduction of costs or expenses.

"Attributable Revenue" means the portion of Gross Revenue arising from
products or services that incorporate, are enabled by, or substantially
depend on the Software. Where the Software is one component among several,
Attributable Revenue may be apportioned in good faith by a documented,
consistently applied methodology.

"Fiscal Year" means Your fiscal year for financial reporting purposes.

