12. TERMINATION AND CURE
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

12.1 Any violation of this license's conditions terminates Your license
     automatically, subject to the cure provisions below.
12.2 NOTICES CURE: For Your first violation of Section 6, Your license is
     reinstated retroactively if You take all practical steps to comply
     within thirty (30) days of learning of the violation.
12.3 PAYMENT CURE: For late, incomplete, or incorrect contributions or
     reports under Section 8, Your license is reinstated retroactively if
     You correct the deficiency in full within sixty (60) days of written
     notice from Licensor.
12.4 No cure is available for a violation of Section 11, for repeated
     violations of the same provision after a prior cure, or for knowing and
     willful violations.
12.5 Sections 10, 15, 16, and 17 survive any termination.

