14. AUDIT
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

No more than once in any twelve (12) month period, and on at least thirty (30)
days' written notice, Licensor may engage an independent third-party auditor,
bound by confidentiality, to verify Your compliance with Section 8 against
Your relevant financial records. The audit will be at Licensor's expense,
except that if it reveals underreporting of more than ten percent (10%) for
any Fiscal Year, You will bear the reasonable cost of the audit in addition to
paying the deficiency.

